product.title: Japanese Sakura Pagoda Osaka Castle Tapestry
product.body_html:
• Description
  • FAQ
  • Shipping

  • Let your imagination take you to Japan with our tapestry

    The Japanese Sakura Pagoda Osaka Castle Tapestry features stunning artwork depicting the beautiful sakura trees and Osaka Castle. It‘s perfect for adding a touch of elegance to living room and bedroom settings.

    A high-quality lightweight tapestry made from 100% polyester, which can be hung up easily. Whether you are covering a part of your wall or hiding clutter this is the perfect tapestry for all your needs. Round colored stickers are provided so you can stick your tapestry up hassle-free.

    Choose from 12 different designs. The color may be different from the photos we show, due to lighting, shadows, and how it is displayed on your screen.

    Measurements
    37x28in / 95x73cm
    59x39in / 150x100cm
    59x51in / 150x130cm
    59x59in / 150x150cm
    78x59in / 200x150cm
    90x59in / 230x150cm
    90x70in / 230x180cm
    117x70in / 300x180cm

    Measurements may be off by 1-5cm for rounding up to a whole number.

    Grab a few tapestries to kawaiify your room

    Wall tapestries can truly transform your room. If you are looking for that kawaii vibe then you've found the right items to add to your list. Combine these with some memo pads, postcards, and wall organisers to complete the look.

    Features

    🌸 Crafted from 100% premium polyester with hand-sewn finishes
    🌸 Suitable for indoor and outdoor use
    🌸 Machine wash cold on gentle cycle, tumble dry low
    🌸 Includes 1 tapestry only
    🌸 12 Japanese-themed designs
    🌸 Round stickers provided to hang the tapestry 



  • Do you ship worldwide? Yes, we ship to over 300 countries and are proud to provide free shipping to the United States, the United Kingdom, Australia, New Zealand, and many countries in Europe.


  • FREE Tracked Shipping to the United States, United Kingdom, Australia, New Zealand, Germany, Spain, France, Italy, Austria, Netherlands, and many more. Find out more here: Shipping Policy.


    Packaging time: 1-3 Business days

    Shipping time: 5-20 Business days
